      "edge": "JournalEntry -> BillingDocument (posted_for)",
      "reason": "DUPLICATE: This edge joined via BillingDocument.accounting_document_id (alternate key). A second edge JournalEntry→BillingDocument (references_invoice) joins via BillingDocument.billing_document_id (PK). Data validation confirmed both paths produce 100% identical results for all 123/123 JE records — zero divergence. The PK-based path (references_invoice) is preferred as it uses the canonical primary key join."
    }
